Setiabudi Sky Garden is a residential comprising of 2 luxurious condominium towers that are adjacent to a service apartment. The buildings feature the largest open air area in Jakarta CBD. It is located in one of the busiest business districts of Jakarta, near Embassies office buildings and international hospitals. Setiabudi Sky Garden built with the&nbsp;concept of an equilibrium state between you, family, nature, and community. The property&nbsp;is only 5 minutes away from Grand Indonesia Shopping Town and Plaza Indonesia Shopping Center which will be great places in your leisure time.<br />
<br />
The apartment indulges you with luxurious facilities, including jogging track, thematic garden, swimming pool, kid&#39;s pool, basketball court, and 24-hour security. The units are spacious two-bed rooms and three-bed rooms. Setiabudi Sky Garden dedicates part of its area for green area. Setiabudi Sky Garden a is a premium apartment which offers peace and serenity for you along with your family.&nbsp;

meta.desc_in:
Seperti namanya, Apartemen Southgate TB Simatupang memiliki lokasi yang sangat strategis di Jakarta Selatan. Karena dekat dengan beberapa pintu tol, antara lain exit Tol Pondok Indah - Pasar Minggu, dan juga TMII/ Cawang exit tol Pasar Minggu.<br />
Apartemen Southgate TB Simatupang dibangun di atas lahan seluas 5,4 hektar dan dilengkapi dengan beragam fasilitas, antara lain jogging track, area BBQ, taman bermain anak- anak, outdoor gym, lapangan tenis, lapangan basket, yoga, kolam renang anak, sauna, taman, lapangan golf mini, dan masih banyak lagi.<br />
Tipe unit yang tersedia di Apartemen Southgate TB Simatupang juga beragam, termasuk tipe unit 1 bedroom + Study (72m2), tipe unit 2 bedroom (103 m2), dan tipe unit 2 bedroom + maid room (101 m2).&nbsp;

meta.desc_en:
Best Western Mangga Dua Hotel and Residence is a mixed development where residences end at the 25th storey while hotel rooms being on the 26th. It is close to the computer and gadget centers of Mangga Dua. Minutes away to Dufan Ancol Theme Parks, train station, and also schools and universities like Universitas Tarumanagara, Universitas Trisakti, Gandhi International School, etc.&nbsp;The tallest building in Mangga Dua,&nbsp;the Best Western Mangga Dua is a perfect choice for home.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
One building with 4 star Hotel, Best Western Mangga Dua offers luxurious facilities such as indoor swimming pool, spa and massage, restaurant, security 24 hours, and equipped with 4 high speed lifts. You can choose from 1-bedrooms, 2-bedrooms, or 3-bedrooms in which all rooms are already fully furnished. Best Western Mangga Dua indulges you with all the comfort and hospitality so you can enjoy all of the hotel facilities with the medium-end price.&nbsp;

meta.desc_in:
Terletak di Dago, Apartemen Grand Dago menyediakan sekitar 3000 Rusunami. Grand Dago Apartment terletak di lokasi yang sangat strategis, dimana banyak universitas, rumah sakit dan sekolah terkenal di sekitar apartemen. Dago merupakan area yang populer serta sejuk dan hijau, saat ini Dago sudah menjadi pusat wisata kuliner, pusat wisata belanja dan pusat berbagai aktivitas bisnis.&nbsp; Grand Dago menyediakan 3000 unit type Studio dengan pilihan luas mulai dari 18 meter persegi hingga 42 meter persegi. Selain itu, apartemen ini juga&nbsp;dilengkapi berbagai fasilitas yang dapat menunjang kenyamanan hidup. Fasilitas yang teresedia adalah area komersial, kolam renang, jalur jogging, panggung pertunjukan serta taman tematik.<br />
<br />
Grand Dago merupakan apartemen dengan harga yang sangat terjangkau serta berkonsep pertama di Indonesia yang memberikan fasilitas musik, dimana setiap unit apartment akan kepingan CD Original Musik Indonesia dan sebuah CD Player di setiap unitnya.&nbsp;Setiap lobby apartment akan bernuansakan musik Indonesia dengan memutarkan lagu-lagu Indonesia dengan dekorasi seperti biografi dan testimoni musisi terutama musisi asal Bandung di setiap dinding apartemen.&nbsp;

meta.desc_en:
As the name implies, Sentraland Bekasi is a residential apartment located in Bekasi, West Java. This apartment has two towers with a total of 1,117 units with a direct view of Mount Salak. This apartment location is strategic due to it is closely located to the Toll Gate Bekasi - Jakarta, shopping centers, hospitals, and schools.<br />
Sentraland Bekasi offers many amenities that are not inferior to five-star hotels, such as 24-hour security, swimming pool, CCTV, jogging track, garden, children playground, an access card, a large parking area, mini market, restaurants, and much else can you enjoy.<br />
Sentraland Bekasi offers various types of unit, including studio room, one bedroom, and 2 bedrooms.&nbsp;

As the name suggests, Lavanya Garden Cinere is an apartment located in Cinere, Depok, West Java. Nevertheless, the location of this apartment is strategic, because it is close to the Lebak Bulus, which has access to several of transportation, toll road, TransJakarta, and MRT (which will be completed in 2018). Also, Lavanya Garden Cinere within close distance to other public facilities, such as international schools, golf courses, office and trade center, supermarkets (Carrefour, Giant, and Hypermart), hospitals with national and international standards, as well as shopping centers.<br />
Lavanya Garden Cinere offers adequate facilities, among others: leisure pool, play pool, lagoon pool, reflexology pool, sunbathing pool, children pool, babies&rsquo; pool, massage pool, fitness center, playground children, garden meditation, jogging track, yoga, BBQ area, and much more.<br />
The types of units that available is also varied, namely the type of studio, 1 bedroom unit type, unit type 2 bedroom, and many more.&nbsp;
